                    ->default(5),
            ]),
    ])
    ->columnSpanFull(),
```

### Tab-Based Form Restructure
```php
Tabs::make(''EnergyLog'')
    ->tabs([
        Tabs\\Tab::make(''Overview'')
            ->icon(''heroicon-o-calendar-days'')
            ->schema([
