- Spatial audio raycasts: max 4 per frame (staggered across frames)

## Event Priority Tiers
| Priority | Type              | Steal Mode    |
|----------|-------------------|---------------|
| 0 (High) | UI, Player VO     | Never stolen  |
| 1        | Player SFX        | Steal quietest|
| 2        | Combat SFX        | Steal farthest|
