| A      |      |      |                 |
| B      |      |      |                 |

## Consequences
- Positive: [benefits]
- Negative: [trade-offs we accept]
- Governor limits affected: [specific limits and headroom remaining]

## Review Date: [when to revisit]
```

## Integration Pattern Template

